{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "biz_dev", "channel": "lead_prospecting", "user": "liam_patel", "message": "Hi team, just an update - we've managed to secure a meeting with potential clients from the Nova Scotia region next week. Let's prepare the deck.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "biz_dev", "channel": "lead_prospecting", "user": "john_smith", "message": "Great work, Liam! Let's include the latest virtual healthcare statistics in our presentation. We need to highlight how our services can meet their needs.", "created_at": 1620500600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "crm_team", "channel": "crm_usage", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Just a reminder, we are having a training session on the new features of our CRM system tomorrow at 2 PM. Please confirm your attendance.", "created_at": 1620501200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "biz_dev", "channel": "lead_prospecting", "user": "liam_patel", "message": "Absolutely, John. I'll ensure that our stats are up-to-date and compelling. Also, should we consider showcasing some case studies?", "created_at": 1620501800000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "crm_team", "channel": "crm_usage", "user": "liam_patel", "message": "Thanks for the reminder, Jane. I'll be there for the CRM training, looking forward to learning more about the new features.", "created_at": 1620502400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "biz_dev", "channel": "lead_prospecting", "user": "john_smith", "message": "Good suggestion, Liam. Let's include some case studies that illustrate the positive impact of our virtual healthcare services. This could be a powerful tool for persuasion.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "crm_team", "channel": "crm_usage", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Great, Liam. I'll share the agenda and the webinar link later today. Make sure you have the CRM software updated to the latest version before the session.", "created_at": 1620503600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "biz_dev", "channel": "lead_prospecting", "user": "liam_patel", "message": "Hello team, I've been looking at some trends and reports today and I came across an interesting article in WTT Solutions. It talks about how CRM software is trending and how it can analyze certain business data that could potentially help grow our virtual healthcare clientele.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "crm_team", "channel": "crm_usage", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "That's interesting, Liam. Currently, our usage of the CRM system is primarily to manage patient information and organize marketing strategies. However, it does have capabilities for data analysis that we might not be fully utilizing.", "create_at": 1620500000100}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "biz_dev", "channel": "lead_prospecting", "user": "john_smith", "message": "I think we need to consider this. We conducted a survey in January, and no one from our team indicated they knew about these analysis capabilities of the CRM system. If it can provide insights that could help us improve our strategies and drive sales into 2026, we should certainly explore this further.", "create_at": 1620500000200}}
